    "abstract": "<jats:title>Abstract</jats:title>\n                <jats:p>Obesity may downregulate vaccine-induced immunogenicity, but the epidemiological evidence for the COVID-19 vaccine is limited, and the sex-associated difference is unknown. It was observed that a higher body mass index was associated with lower titers of spike IgG antibodies against SARS-CoV-2 in men but not in women.</jats:p>",
